Family and friends have gathered at the University of Johannesburg campus in Soweto for a Special Official Funeral of business mogul, Richard Maponya. JOHANNESBURG - The country bids farewell to business mogul, Richard Maponya. READ: Richard Maponya dies aged 99 Family and friends have gathered at the University of Johannesburg campus in Soweto for a Special Official Funeral on Tuesday. Maponya passed away last week at the age of 99 